## Ender Chest

---



[Entity Action Type](https://origins.readthedocs.io/en/latest/types/entity_action_types/ender_chest)

Brings up the Ender Chest GUI as if the player has interacted with one.

Type ID: `origins:ender_chest`




---

### Examples

```json
"entity_action": {
    "type": "origins:ender_chest"
}
```
